org.dedda.games.scheisse.tool

Class Parse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dedda.games.scheisse.tool.Parse

  • public abstract class Parse
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for parsing Strings to numbers or number based objects such as Dimensions and casting numbers to a different types.

    Created by dedda on 5/22/14.
